explains: v. 复制，翻印；模拟；再制造，再现；繁殖，生殖

sentences.en: Most reptiles reproduce by laying eggs on land.
sentences.cn: 大多数爬行动物通过在陆地产卵进行繁殖。

sentences.en: The movie makes no pretension to reproduce life.
sentences.cn: 这部电影并未标榜重现了真实生活。

sentences.en: One of the new models has the facility to reproduce speech as well as text.
sentences.cn: 新款型中的一款有复制言语和文本的附加功能。
